channel.title: Quick queston about getting new client
channel.description:
I got 366 client (mopars new one) and for my dream server im making your ganna need the latest latest client (one with zombie clothes and zombie emotes)
so if I wanted to get a new client would I just copy the newest cache from file store 32 and replace it with the cache 366 or 363 (windscape) cache? would that work too?
